{"tid":2233920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角警署獲批續領酒牌兩年 居民上訴  委員會稱沒證據警員飲酒後騷擾街坊","createTime":"2020-10-07T13:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T13:09:22.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75e25000fe523f7cab4b0cd72f9097fb575744fc","tid":2233920,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:09:22.000Z","msg":"旺角警署警官餐廳早前獲批續領酒牌兩年，油尖旺區議員林兆彬及 76 名住在警署附近的居民上訴，市政服務上訴委員會今（7日）聆訊。林兆彬稱，早前有過千市民聯署反對續牌，反對民意清晰；委員會主席王鳴峰則表示，酒牌局批酒牌與否，無關持牌人的民意高低，他亦多番質疑，「有無證據有警察在該餐廳飲酒後，騷擾街坊？」委員會終決定押後裁決，其後以書面通知結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E7%BA%8C%E9%85%92%E7%89%8C%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0-%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E7%BA%8C%E7%89%8C%E7%84%A1%E9%97%9C%E6%8C%81%E7%89%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8E/?fbclid=IwAR1tvIn_1i7fgzOnfShRi9JqCYA-0WrgM9BxOGDPsyPxwciP7TJrkb8KM0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%2585%2592%25E7%2589%258C%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2599%25B0-%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%2589%258C%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E4%25BD%258E%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1tvIn_1i7fgzOnfShRi9JqCYA-0WrgM9BxOGDPsyPxwciP7TJrkb8KM0w&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=a5ee0751\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E9%2